title: Ep. 627 - Popatlal Deceives The Competitors - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The first competition takes place. Popatlal sticks the lemon to the spoon hence does not win the competition. Sonu wins it following which Tapu comes second. Baga and Nattu Kaka announce the next competition.

title: Ep. 628 - Tough Competition And Competitors - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sodhi wins the next task following which Champaklal comes second. Sunder wins the reverse race task, Daya cheers for him.  Judges reveal the next task to be The arm-wrestling competition.

title: Ep. 629 - The Arm Wrestlers - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham is excited about the arm wrestling competition. Bhide tries to put a scheme and Madhvi wins the round against Anjali. Champaklal wins his round against Abdul which surprises everyone. Jethalal is confused about whom to cheer for.

title: Ep. 630 - The Ambiguity Of The Winners - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Komal wins the final round against Daya. Next in the pipeline are Popatlal against Haathi. There is tough competition between them. It would be really interesting to see who wins the round.

title: Ep. 631 - Guess Who's The Winner? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal wins the last arm wrestling round against Haathi and shocks everyone. He explains everyone as how there is a technique for this game to win. All the winners are announced. All the participants are tired and have bad body ache the next day.

title: Ep. 632 - Tasks For The Ladies - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham Khel Mahotsav continues. The next competition is for all the married couples. Ladies are being challenged so as to who would be the ones to complete the task in lesser time.

title: Ep. 633 - Baga Maintains The Suspense - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Baga and Nattu Kaka take time to announce the winners. Jethalal and Daya being the winners, dance to the tunes. The next competition is 'Blast the balloon'. Everyone tries their best.

title: Ep. 634 - Bursting The Balloon Competition - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal and Champaklal could not burst a single balloon and so couldn't Dr. Haathi and his wife. Sunderlal and Popatlal win the competition following which Anjali and Taarak come second. Daya and Tapu come third.

title: Ep. 635 - The Last Task  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Judges confess that they are not aware of the final competition. The last task is decided by Champaklal and Tapu. Judges' announcement shock everyone.

title: Ep. 636 - A Special Kid Visits Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Someone visits Gokuldham on the last day of GKM and tells them how he loves everyone here. Sunderlal identifies him. He jokes around and the whole society bursts out laughing. Gokuldham Khel Ratna awardee is yet to be announced.

title: Ep. 637 - Champaklal Wins The GKM - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: GKM comes to an end with Champaklal winning the Khel Mahotsav. Champaklal gets a call from his friend so he calls him over. Daya and Tapu ask Sunder to stay at their place for a week.

title: Ep. 638 - A Bad Day For Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal could not have breakfast as Sunder ate them all. Sunder's friends arrive and create chaos. Jethalal could not focus on anything but food. He thought of ordering food but the phone is not working.

title: Ep. 639 - Sunder Has A Deal For Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal avoids taking calls from Sunder. Sunder reveals his deal plan to Jetha who declined to it. Jethalal is irritated with everyone. He increases the working hours of Nattu Kaka.

title: Ep. 640 - Jethalal Gets Stuck In His Godown - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal is talking on the phone in his godown's bathroom and suddenly the phone falls. He does not understand what to do and comes out for help. He finds himself locked in his godown. Watch the funny episode to know what will happen next.

title: Ep. 641 - Daya Is Worried For Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal was supposed to go to the airport, but when Daya is unable to contact him, she gets worried. They try to call Nathu Kaka to know Jethalal's whereabouts.
